name: THE SENSE OF LIGHT
description:
Feel the light in your heart.

It was a happy party for orphan kids who were living under the protection of the Child Foundation. We were photographers in there, capturing their happy moments. The weather was so warm and created these shapes out of shadow and light, Zac was sitting next to me and the flames of the sun were trying to burn her freckled skin. I captured this shot with my eyes before even I touch my camera.
